divs: Sighting DetailsComing off of an off ramp, I stopped at a light and I noticed an object flying between the stoplights. I thought at first it was a helicopter, but observing it I did not notice the usual features of a helicopter. I took a picture with my cell phone and by then the light changed and I had to turn, I tried to follow it but could not. I hope the picture helps.
Summary: Was at a light and noticed an object passing between the lights.
